{"id":"q-poly-05","unit":"polynomials","difficulty":"hard","question":"已知 f(x) = x⁴ - 5x² + 4，求所有實根","options":["±1、±2","±1","±2","無實根"],"answer":0,"explanation":"令 y=x²，得 y²-5y+4=(y-1)(y-4)=0，故 y=1 或 4，對應 x=±1、±2。"},
